<sect1 id="graph_template_page_1graph_template_topology">
<title>Topology</title>
<para>The topology function defines edge connections:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal">define_topology([](<ref refid="classparticle__template" kindref="compound">particle_template</ref>*<sp/>p1,<sp/><ref refid="classparticle__template" kindref="compound">particle_template</ref>*<sp/>p2)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Return<sp/>true<sp/>if<sp/>p1<sp/>and<sp/>p2<sp/>should<sp/>be<sp/>connected</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Example:<sp/>only<sp/>connect<sp/>different<sp/>particles</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>p1<sp/>!=<sp/>p2;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">});</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
